private getRecoveryBudget(): number {
  const contextLimit = this.compactionConfig.contextLimit;
  if (contextLimit <= 0) {
    return 0;  // unlimited — 어떤 감소든 성공
  }

  const reserveTokens = this.compactionConfig.reserveTokens;
  if (reserveTokens > 0) {
    const budget = contextLimit - reserveTokens;
    return budget > 0 ? budget : Math.floor(contextLimit * 0.95);
  }
  return Math.floor(contextLimit * 0.95);
}
```

**문제**: `reserveTokens > 0`일 때 `budget = contextLimit - reserveTokens`
- 이 budget은 "압축 후 목표 토큰"인데, 실제론 `reserveTokens`만큼 여유가 있어야 함
